msgctxt "2136"
msgid "Broke-ass College Student"
msgstr "Universitario en quiebra"

msgctxt "2140"
msgid "Saejima"
msgstr "Saejima"

msgctxt "2144"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "2148"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "100_Broke-ass College Student"
msgid "What was with those maniacs chasing that girl around?\\r\n"\n"Just when you think the city's dangerous enough as is..."
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con esos locos persiguiendo a esa chica?\\r\n"\n"Justo cuando creía que la ciudad ya era lo bastante peligrosa..."

msgctxt "112_Broke-ass College Student"
msgid "I wonder if she's okay? Maybe I should've called the police."
msgstr "¿Estará bien? Quizás debí haber llamado a la policía."

msgctxt "124_Saejima"
msgid "Hey, that girl ya saw bein' chased...\\r\n"\n"she wearin' a black jacket?"
msgstr "¿Oye, esa chica a la que perseguían...\\r\n"\n"llevaba una chaqueta negra?"

msgctxt "136_Broke-ass College Student"
msgid "Huh? Oh, uh... yeah, I think so."
msgstr "¿Eh? Oh... Sí, creo que sí."

msgctxt "148_Saejima"
msgid "That'd be Makiko. You see where she went?"
msgstr "Ha de ser Makiko. ¿Has visto por donde se fue?"

msgctxt "160_Broke-ass College Student"
msgid "She went running along this road toward Shichifuku Street.\\r\n"\n"Should I notify the police?"
msgstr "Se fue corriendo por esta calle hacia la calle Shichifuku.\\r\n"\n"¿Debería llamar a la policía?"

msgctxt "172_Saejima"
msgid "Nah, don't bother callin' the cops. I'll take care of this.\\r\n"\n"She was headed toward West Park, yeah? Thanks, kid."
msgstr "Nah, ni te molestes en llamar a la policía. Yo me encargo.\\r\n"\n"¿Iba hacia el Parque Oeste, verdad? Gracias, chico."

msgctxt "196_Broke-ass College Student"
msgid "If you're still looking for that girl in the black jacket,\\r\n"\n"she was running down this road toward Shichifuku Street."
msgstr "Si sigues buscando a la chica de la chaqueta negra,\\r\n"\n"Se fue corriendo por esta calle hacia la calle Shichifuku."

